reviewText: if you watch dog the bounty hunter on tv then it worth purching the first two seasons of dog the bounty hunter. the thing is it's not the full season but the best of the fist two seasons of the tv show. the wedding dvd is only of the day and days leading up to the day that dog and beth got married. it is worth the money to purchase the dvd's in this set insteed of buying the dvd's one by one.
